  "texts": [
    "Other researchers have studied positive and negative comments [165], young and old voices [177], familiar and unfamiliar voices [171], warning voices [176], and different emotion regulation strategies to intervene driver emotions [181,182].",
    "In sum, auditory intervention may be an effective way to regulate the driver's emotions while rarely leading to distraction.",
    "V2X-Based Human Emotion RegulationSeamless and real-time decisions of emotion regulation can be obtained in V2X, where drivers can be aware of their neighbors' emotions in the situated environment by communicating with intelligent traffic participants such as the cloud [183,184] and neighboring vehicles [185].In Ref.",
    "[183], a crowd-cloud collaborative and situationaware music recommendation system is designed to diminish drivers' negative emotions.",
    "The sensing data and the driver's social information are collected and processed by the in-car smartphone."
